  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Get a headlock on fun with Hal Wrestling! Eight rompin', stompin' brutes squares off in a head-to-head matches any sports fan can enjoy! All the pro wrestling moves you can use and a few you haven't seen before! Go one-on-one against the computer or a friend, or round up your own four-man wrecking crew for thunderous action! Hal Wrestling - we're coming to get YOU!",
